name: The Ensor Chair
description: The sleek lines and unique upholstery of the Ensor accord it a certain distinction, offering a refined yet bold addition to your dining scheme. A clean-lined base, deep seat and solid backrest for comfort lend the Ensor a sense of high-end sophistication. With its tapering legs, each finished in a dark-tinted beech, this design exhibits a clear eye for style. As with the rest of the chairs from the DAVIDSON collection, this chair can be upholstered in a range of fabrics and leathers of your choice to perfectly suit your interior.
